Network Mapping and Packet Capture and Analysis
--------------------------------------------------------------------------


		Table of Content
	------------------------
	1. Intro











1. Intro

	This AI is meant not as a replacement for IDS/IPS--such as Anomaly based intrusion detection--but rather as an addition to the toolbox. NemPac is made of three modules:
			1.  Packet Capture Module
			2.  Network Mapping Module
			3.  AI Comparison Module

	Using NemPac you can easily monitor for new devices connected to a local network, and abnormal network traffic.


